public abstract class IntIterator
extends AbstractLiteralIterator

Abstract LiteralIterator implementation that supports an iteration over int values. Subclasses need only implement the nextInt() method. The nextLong(), nextFloat(), and nextDouble() methods all simply cast the output of nextInt(). The next() method simply wraps the output of nextInt() in an Integer object.

作者：
jeffrey heer
